<item>
            <title>[LU-8708] Grant shrinking disabled all the time</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8708</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It appears that OBD_CONNECT_GRANT_SHRINK is not set by client at all. It was disabled all the way back in 1.8.1 time due to bz 19507 &quot;for debugging&quot; and never reenabled. Commit a3c09ef128651a8f041171f2d6099b3ba8d8f2c6.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I guess that was an omission and we should reenable it back?&lt;br/&gt;
Do we still need it in master in light of grant_param stuff? I think we still do?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
